init_text: When you die, you appear in a cinema with a number of other people who look like you. You find out that they are your previous reincarnations, and soon you all begin watching your next life on the big screen.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You see yourself as a baby, and then as a child, and then as a teenager, and so on.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You wonder if they are watching their own lives, or if they are watching yours.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: It's the voice of the cinema manager.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You turn to the cinema manager, who is sitting in the corner of the cinema.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: "So what are we doing here?" you ask.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: "Why didn't you show me how I died?" you ask.
